CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. 13 reads: "Daisy E. Lampkin Lauded for Service to Mankind At Colorful Testimonial in Webster Hall - Out-Of-Town Guests...Others are Mrs. Mame Mason, Loraine, Ohio; Mrs. Robert Thomas, Oberlin, Ohio; Mrs. Beatrice Batch Hartley, Monongahela, and Mr. and Mrs. John Morsell, New York City. - All Photos by Teenie Harris"
TitMainTitle: Mame Mason, Mrs. Robert Thomas, Beatrice Batch Hartley, Mrs. Morsell, and John Morsell standing in Webster Hall for banquet honoring Daisy Lampkin
